preference.name: PortalPSEColumnsShownPref
preference.preference_description: Specifies the list of Structure Manager columns displayed from left-to-right. To display the Explore Checked Out property, add the bl_rev_expl_checkout value to this list. Depending on your system configuration, you may also have to set the PSEDisplayNameWithTypeColumnsShownPref preference. Valid Values: Accepts multiple strings as values. It must be a valid BOM line property.
